1) Create a Recovery Services vault.
2) Configure a backup of VM, created at 1st day with automatic backup each
Saturday at 00:00 GMT.
3) Create Azure File Share.
4) Connect new File Share as drive X: to VM, created at 1st day, using
Custom script extension.
5) Create new role with modify permissions, assign it to resource group with
VM and add account epmcourse@outlook.com to it.
